                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While testing patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/23814&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/23814&lt;/a&gt; on master branch, sanity-hsm test 220a failed in review-zfs-part-1 test session as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-hsm test 220a: Changelog for failed archive ================================================ 21:02:02 (1483333322)
CMD: onyx-67 pkill -CONT -x lhsmtool_posix
Purging archive on onyx-67
CMD: onyx-67 rm -rf /tmp/arc1/shsm/*
Starting copytool agt1 on onyx-67
CMD: onyx-67 mkdir -p /tmp/arc1/shsm/
CMD: onyx-67 lhsmtool_posix  --daemon --hsm-root /tmp/arc1/shsm --bandwidth 1 /mnt/lustre2 &amp;lt; /dev/null &amp;gt; /logdir/test_logs/2017-01-01/lustre-reviews-el7-x86_64--review-zfs-part-1--1_8_1__43327__-70254280473480-124930/sanity-hsm.test_220a.copytool_log.onyx-67.log 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
CMD: onyx-64 /usr/sbin/lctl --device lustre-MDT0000 changelog_register -n
CMD: onyx-64 lctl set_param mdd.lustre-MDT0000.changelog_mask=+hsm
mdd.lustre-MDT0000.changelog_mask=+hsm
CMD: onyx-67 pkill -STOP -x lhsmtool_posix
Copytool is suspended on onyx-67
CMD: onyx-67 pkill -CONT -x lhsmtool_posix
Copytool is continued on onyx-67
CMD: onyx-64 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm.actions | awk &apos;/&apos;0x200000402:0x221:0x0&apos;.*action=&apos;ARCHIVE&apos;/ {print \$13}&apos; | cut -f2 -d=
CMD: onyx-64 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm.actions | awk &apos;/&apos;0x200000402:0x221:0x0&apos;.*action=&apos;ARCHIVE&apos;/ {print \$13}&apos; | cut -f2 -d=
CMD: onyx-64 lctl --device lustre-MDT0000 changelog_deregister cl2
lustre-MDT0000: Deregistered changelog user &apos;cl2&apos;
